    <title>Logitech’s affordable new low-profile keyboard also fits Cherry MX-style keycaps</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="A user holds the Logitech G515 keyboard in one hand in front a computer setup featuring neon lighting." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Pb35QatWYIW0TCFjAWMfi_2J0Zs=/0x0:2794x1863/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73425980/logitech_g515_keyboard2.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Logitech G G515 Lightspeed TKL wireless keyboard is just 22mm thick and features upgraded MX-compatible keycaps.&lt;/em&gt; | Image: Logitech&lt;/figcaption&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;

  &lt;p id="ro4ZYE"&gt;Logitech has announced a new low-profile gaming keyboard, the &lt;a href="https://imp.i125364.net/c/482924/795933/11355?u=http%3A%2F%2Flogitechg.com%2Fg515&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;G515 Lightspeed TKL Wireless&lt;/a&gt;, featuring upgraded low-profile switches that are now compatible with Cherry MX-style keycaps, improving the keyboard’s customizability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="jV0yXO"&gt;The G515 is a welcome upgrade to &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/circuitbreaker/2019/8/15/20806746/logitech-g915-g815-low-profile-mechanical-keyboard-romer-gl-switches-release-date-news-features"&gt;Logitech’s G915 Lightspeed Wireless&lt;/a&gt; keyboard, which debuted in 2019. The new G515 features a TKL (tenkeyless) design that’s similar to the smaller &lt;a href="https://imp.i125364.net/c/482924/795933/11355?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.logitechg.com%2Fen-us%2Fproducts%2Fgaming-keyboards%2Fg915-tkl-wireless.html&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Logitech G915 TKL update&lt;/a&gt; from 2020; this one completely eliminates not only the G915’s number pad but also the wide volume wheel that sat above it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="OiQmBI"&gt;Saying goodbye to that physical volume wheel leaves the G515 keyboard, which should be available today, with a $139 price tag that’s significantly cheaper than both the &lt;a href="https://imp.i125364.net/c/482924/795933/11355?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.logitechg.com%2Fen-us%2Fproducts%2Fgaming-keyboards%2Fg915-low-profile-wireless-mechanical-gaming-keyboard.html%3Fsp%3D2%26searchclick%3Dlogi&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;$249.99 G915&lt;/a&gt; and the...&lt;/p&gt;
